✨Welcome back to a new semester, bears! Womxn in Math is back for a new semester, and we are recruiting!✨

If you would like to learn more about us, please come out to our tabling events:

Tabling: Friday, January 22nd, 5-7pm PST
Calapalooza Day 1: Monday, January 25th, 5-7pm PST
Calapalooza Day 2: Tuesday, January 26th, 5-7pm PST
Calapalooza Day 3: Wednesday, January 27th, 5-7pm PST

Link: https://berkeley.zoom.us/j/7783198405

We are also holding two info sessions, where you can learn more about us, our plans for this semester, and how to get involved!

Info session 1:
Thursday, February 4th, 6-7pm PST
Zoom: https://berkeley.zoom.us/j/7783198405

Info session 2: 
Friday, February 5th, 6-7pm PST
Zoom:  https://berkeley.zoom.us/j/7783198405

If you have any questions, feel free to email us and check out our social media:

email: ucbwim@gmail.com

website: https://wim.berkeley.edu/

facebook: https://www.facebook.com/WIMatUCB/

instagram: https://www.instagram.com/ucbwim/
